# AUDIO::SET_AMBIENT_VOICE_NAME_HASH

## Summary
Sets a ped to use a specific voice different to the one associated with their model

## Parameters
* **PED_INDEX** ped
* **INT** voiceNameHash

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
VoiceName specified by Audio
